            <h3>What is Green World Academy?</h3>
            <p>
              Green World Academy is a forward-thinking institution dedicated to
              providing holistic education that blends academic excellence with
              environmental awareness. Our goal is to nurture students who
              thrive both intellectually and socially while being responsible
