            </p>

            <h3>Why Choose Green World Academy?</h3>
            <p>
              Enrolling at Green World Academy offers numerous advantages. We
              provide a comprehensive curriculum that combines traditional
              academics with eco-friendly practices, ensuring a balanced
              education. With small class sizes and experienced educators,
              students receive personalized attention in a nurturing
              environment. Our campus includes smart classrooms, green spaces,
              and sustainable infrastructure to enhance learning.
            </p>

            <h3>What Sets Us Apart?</h3>
            <p>
              We prioritize character development, leadership, and community
              involvement, preparing students to excel not only academically but
              also in life. Through diverse extracurricular activities, we
              encourage creativity, teamwork, and innovation. At Green World
              Academy, your child will gain an education that prepares them to
              make a meaningful difference in the world.
            </p>

            <h3>What Extracurricular Opportunities Are Available?</h3>
            <p>
              Our academy offers a wide range of extracurricular activities
              designed to help students explore their passions and develop new
              skills. From sports and arts to science clubs and environmental
              projects, we ensure that every student has opportunities to grow
              beyond academics.
            </p>

            <h3>How Do We Support Student Well-being?</h3>
            <p>
              Student well-being is at the heart of our approach. We offer
              counseling services, health programs, and a supportive environment
              where students can feel safe and valued. Our focus on mental,
              emotional, and social well-being ensures that students can thrive
              both inside and outside the classroom.
            </p>
